original: Öhman, Karl Åke, tandläkare, Kisa, f. 15/5/17 i Nyköping av dir. E. Ö. o. Magda Östergren. G. 42 m. Maja Sörme. Barn: Lars-Åke f. 43. — Stud:-ex. i Sthlm 36, tand :läk :ex. 42. Egen prakt, i Kisa fr. 42.
translated: Öhman, Karl Åke, dentist, Kisa, born on May 15, 1917 in Nyköping to director E. Ö. and Magda Östergren. Married in 1942 to Maja Sörme. Children: Lars-Åke, born in 1943. Passed high school exams in Stockholm in 1936, dental exams in 1942. Started own practice in Kisa from 1942.
